stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> NoBotComment
  NoBotComment --> PostFresh: full agentic triage
  PostFresh --> BotCommented
  BotCommented --> Validate: next run
  Validate --> Unchanged: same conclusion
  Validate --> DriftPosted: changed with high confidence
  Validate --> ConflictNeedsReview: changed with weak evidence
  Unchanged --> BotCommented
  BotCommented --> HumanResponded: human comments after bot
  HumanResponded --> LearnAndSkip: record feedback, no bot comment
  LearnAndSkip --> HumanResponded
